 to - I don't know. He could cook mind, my father could, my mother was ill, you know - or anything like that, yes, he could do a bit of cooking. But I don't - I don't remember doing much - much work cleaning I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Would he wash up?
