 and very often - he wouldn't come home to dinner when we were old enough used to take a - dinner down to him at the docks. Yes. My sister and I. We used to take my father's dinner down because his chest was bad, he couldn't - walk a lot back and fore and
 we used to save him walking, we used to go down the dock with his dinner. And - my mother used to put it in a basin you know like, whatever it was for, and I can always remember tying it up in a - a -
