Only in a school like you know. Not much like. I couldn't run very well either. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Did you go to any theatres?
