ty often, you know, pretty often, like normal - my father'd take us over there for a walk sometimes see, it wasn't very far, when we were small. And my mother had no relations really - in - Aberafan. They were all in Britain Ferry see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Would you go and see them at all?
