Yes, we - I used to go over - well very seldom, in the holiday time perhaps my mother might take - one of us over you know. But she used to go over very often, my mother, if she could manage it. You know, to go and see her sister 
like. By train then, but it was only - a couple of coppers it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Did your parents have any friends?
