Yes. Yes. People living by here you know, yes, very friendly and the neighbours are very friendly here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Where would they see their friends?
