\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9595179 CH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 Well - I mean there was
 - only - there was nothing much like you know - the only thing used to do, she had a friend, used to go to the pictures perhaps once a week you know, or - otherwise like - with their friend - their neighbour - the end house, had a lot of children, and as
 a gang they would go out for a picnic in the woods, with the children you know, things like that, you know, but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14882485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11821286\charrsid12412112 You'd go like that would you?
