edral church see. When we got married now - signing the register now in the - of the vestry in the church - he put Claude Ellis then see. See for the - and Mr \{BLANK\} now he's awful - man. He said? You didn\rquote 
t tell me that name, he said, when you - put the 
banns in. He said, look here, he said - he said, I could have - not married you through that, he said. 'Cos you've got to put - and he wouldn't put Ellis for anything, that was his name. Claude Ellis Harris see. Well I put Mary Charlotte, that was my name
